      "title": "My latest books cartoon for the Guardian ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s640x960/49b4b6fdcaafd54728ab85b5222b145e736c344f.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"839\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Panel 1 A cartoon book with a face, legs and arms shouts out &quot;Beware! Heatwave reading dangers!&quot;  Panel 2 Caption &quot;Binding glue softened by the sun&quot; Image: The book stands helplessly as its glue drips and pages fall to the floor.  Panel 3 Caption &quot;Dropped while reading in a cooling bath&quot;  Image: The book splashes into the water  Panel 4 Caption &quot;Mislaid by a heat-addled reader&quot; Image: The book gestures wildly as the reader stumbles away in a daze.  Panel 5 Caption &quot;Spontaneous combustion&quot; Image: The book explodes in flame.  Panel 6 &quot;Sweaty hands!&quot; screams the book as it runs away from  a large pink hand, dripping with perspiration.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s75x75_c1/38de7116c47117a2af9006200c704210fa7e243d.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s100x200/f90f7537412973242f4342345d846885bc7fd281.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s250x400/17cb28d0b0d59b778b84e1f149b0665239f3dc58.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s400x600/b5252772002e24ac4790649b53b2d6224631ce5c.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s500x750/b03b909f56122bff0dc40c4dddeb65d25da603db.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s540x810/0fb7e21ed45b8b5d33152bb805e8b1cf0e90de66.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43a5-11/s640x960/49b4b6fdcaafd54728ab85b5222b145e736c344f.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/66863a4a8791af51e3ea65cb71c14a9f/66a6750a553f43