      "title": "My latest Books cartoon for the Guardian",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s640x960/53ff5fed224da97a547395367799f2c1820c4583.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"781\" data-orig-width=\"1400\" alt=\"Title: Presenting My cover designs for a series of Highbrow Literary Novels &#10;&#10;Panel one.&#10;Designer shows a book cover to the publisher. It shows a woman and man looking at a burning house with an orange sky behind.&#10;The publisher says&#10;&quot;Not classy enough!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel Two.&#10;Designer shows a book cover to the publisher. It is now the same image in back and white with a text box hiding the house.&#10;The publisher says&#10;&quot;Better, but not right!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel Three.&#10;Designer shows a book cover to the publisher. It is now just white text on a plain navy blue background&#10;The publisher says&#10;&quot;Yes! But take it further!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel Four.&#10;Designer shows a book cover to the publisher. The author name is now gone too, the title is tiny on plain green.&#10;The publisher says&#10;&quot;So close!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel Five.&#10;Designer shows a book cover to the publisher. It is completely blank, white paper.&#10;The publisher says&#10;&quot;Perfection!&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s75x75_c1/acda6d19703f44037b8937c48207a4aec629324f.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s100x200/7271c7471bd218d51953c0b49619c07839e21874.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s250x400/aa4c8c90622e64e09b02b488e9919b66eb51d66b.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s400x600/32359b14e66bef4aa1760fffa1acfb258a0e1882.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e8b47035e99adedd6f415b862680680/85d55bdb3518b406-0b/s500x750/bc91a86d86c8ac75a069a6f7706bd173d5d38fa1.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr